snippet: Mitchell Starc shone with bat and ball as Australia dismissed Pakistan for 163 to secure an innings and 18-run victory in the second test on Friday, the win giving the hosts an unassailable 2-0 lead in the three-match series....
lead_paragraph: Mitchell Starc shone with bat and ball as Australia dismissed Pakistan for 163 to secure an innings and 18-run victory in the second test on Friday, the win giving the hosts an unassailable 2-0 lead in the three-match series.

headline.main: Starc Brilliance Earns Australia Series Victory
headline.print_headline: Starc Brilliance Earns Australia Series Victory
